high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn right and walk across the room, hang a left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the dirty mug out of the coffee machine on the counter.
Walk over to the sink on your left.
Wash the dirty mug in the sink and then pick it back up.
Turn right and walk back over to where the coffee machine is on the counter.
Put the clean mug in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug in a coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn right, walk forward to the door, then turn left and walk forward to the coffee machine on the counter.
Pick up the mug on the coffee machine.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the mug in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Turn right and walk back to the coffee machine.
Put the mug back on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned mug on a coffee machine.

high_descs: Walk over to the coffee maker
Head back to the coffee maker
Put the cup in the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Fill the cup with water and put it in the coffee maker
